Type: ShinyApp
Title: AI SQL Chatbot (Shiny)
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A lightweight Shiny (bslib) chat interface for natural language
    to SQL data analysis, powered by Claude via the ellmer package. Serves as
    an alternative to the React frontend, calling the same plumber2 API backend
    or using ellmer directly.
Authors@R: person("Developer", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Imports:
    shiny,
    bslib,
    shinychat,
    ellmer,
    DBI,
    RSQLite,
    reactable,
    htmltools,
    httr2,
    rlang
